OL,3,CPoliceman in tears as he is cleared of
OL,4,Ckilling motorist in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,FA police officer burst into tears as
OL,7,Fhe was cleared of killing a motorist
OL,8,Fduring a high-speed pursuit of another
OL,9,Fdriver.
OL,11,FMatthew Pike, 40, was following a
OL,12,Fwhite Volkswagen Tiguan driven by
OL,13,FLewis Griffin through Bristol city
OL,14,Fcentre shortly before midnight on
OL,15,FNovember 4, 2021.
OL,17,FBristol Crown Court heard Pc Pike
OL,18,Freached speeds of up to 93mph in his
OL,19,Funmarked BMW police car as he followed
OL,20,FGriffin.
