OL,3,CPoliceman in tears as he is cleared of
OL,4,Ckilling motorist in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,FThe pursuit ended when Griffin's car
OL,7,Fcollided with a Honda Jazz being
OL,8,Fdriven by Keryl Johnson, 35.
OL,10,FDr Johnson was badly injured in the
OL,11,Fcrash at Newfoundland Circus and died
OL,12,Fseveral days later in hospital.
OL,14,FGriffin, 23, was jailed in February
OL,15,F2024 for eight years after admitting
OL,16,Fcausing death by dangerous driving. He
OL,17,Fwas also banned from driving for 10
OL,18,Fyears.
