OL,3,CPoliceman in tears as he is cleared of
OL,4,Ckilling motorist in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,FPc Pike was later charged with causing
OL,7,Fdeath by dangerous driving, and an
OL,8,Falternative charge of causing death by
OL,9,Fcareless driving.
OL,11,FFollowing legal submissions from Ray
OL,12,FTully KC, representing Pc Pike, Judge
OL,13,FEdward Burgess KC ruled the
OL,14,Fprosecution had not proven its case
OL,15,Fand ordered the jury to find the
OL,16,Fdefendant not guilty of all charges.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
