OL,3,CPoliceman in tears as he is cleared of
OL,4,Ckilling motorist in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,FAddressing the jury, the judge said:
OL,7,F"As you know, on Thursday of last
OL,8,Fweek, the prosecution closed its case,
OL,9,Fmeaning that at that stage they had
OL,10,Fcalled all the evidence they had
OL,11,Fintended to in this trial.
OL,13,F"Over the course of the next few court
OL,14,Fdays, I considered the evidence and
OL,15,Fthe law and considered it with counsel
OL,16,Fon both sides.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
