OL,3,CPoliceman in tears as he is cleared of
OL,4,Ckilling motorist in high-speed pursuit
OL,6,F"On the contrary, put simply he said
OL,7,FMatthew Pike did his job as he was
OL,8,Ftrained to do it.
OL,10,F"As a result, it is my decision that
OL,11,Fon both counts, Matthew Pike must now
OL,12,Fbe found not guilty."
OL,14,FThe judge added: "This is a dreadfully
OL,15,Fdifficult, incredibly sad and utterly
OL,16,Ftragic case.
OL,18,F"So far as the proceedings against
OL,19,FMatthew Pike are concerned at the
OL,20,Fcrown court, they are now at an end."
